rdfs:label: CMusic
ns:common.topic.description: cmusic is an audio compilation language which was created by F. Richard Moore. A full explanation of CMusic can be found in the book Elements of Computer Music, by F. Richard Moore, ISBN 0-13-252552-6.

ns:common.document.text: cmusic is an audio compilation language which was created by F. Richard Moore. A full explanation of CMusic can be found in the book Elements of Computer Music, by F. Richard Moore (Prentice-Hall, 1990), ISBN 0-13-252552-6.
